Subject: Request for MIME media type Application/Vendor Tree - vnd.cups-raw

Name : Michael Sweet

E-mail : mike&easysw.com

MIME media type name : Application

MIME subtype name : Vendor Tree - vnd.cups-raw

Required parameters : None

Optional parameters :
None

Encoding considerations :
Potentially contains raw 8-bit data.

Security considerations :
Since raw data is sent directly to a printer, it is possible to
damage or otherwise render inoperable a printing device.

Interoperability considerations : Used by the Common UNIX Printing
System ("CUPS").  May be used by CUPS or Internet Printing Protocol
("IPP") clients to send printer-specific files to a server.


Published specification :
CUPS-IDD-1.0: Common UNIX Printing System Interface Design
Description.

Available at "http://www.cups.org/documentation.html".


Applications which use this media :
Common UNIX Printing System ("CUPS") servers and clients.
Internet Printing Protocol ("IPP") clients.



Additional information :

1. Magic number(s) :
2. File extension(s) :
3. Macintosh file type code :
This format depends greatly on the destination printer.  Use outside
of internal filters is discouraged.
